Moody's Investors Service Inc said itupgraded Scott Paper Co's long-term debt rating to A-3 fromBaa-1. The company's Prime-2 commercial paper rating remainsunchanged.    Approximately one billion dlrs of long-term debt isaffected.    Moody's said the upgrade reflects Scott's continuingimprovement in operating results, as well as Moody'sexpectation of substantial funds flowing to the company from anasset sale. Reuter&#3;